org.vadere.simulator.models.density

Interface IGaussianFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JGaussianFilter, ObstacleGaussianFilter, PedestrianGaussianFilter

    public interface IGaussianFilter
    IGaussianFilter is a refershable image processing calculator that can be used to solve a discrete convolution or other calculations that can be done by a image processing filter.

        Parameters:
        x - the x-coordinate (for example the x-coordinate of a place on the floor)
